{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"5mqyhqbl70k784qyd7mrkav","title":"Thread Safety","desc":"","updated":1713648775236,"created":1713648406602,"custom":{},"fname":"execution.concurrency.multithreading.thread safety","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"cs"},"contentHash":"fe3852abc234aba3bd4366ecbeafa6f8","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"execution.concurrency.multithreading.thread safety","id":"5mqyhqbl70k784qyd7mrkav","vaultName":"cs"},"value":"execution.concurrency.synchronization","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":4,"offset":368},"end":{"line":9,"column":45,"offset":409},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"execution.concurrency.synchronization"}},{"from":{"fname":"lang.java.concurrency.multithreading.thread safety","id":"3uaj7ngwih7npv8vlfs7k6d","vaultName":"cs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":41,"offset":83},"end":{"line":4,"column":95,"offset":137},"indent":[]},"value":"execution.concurrency.multithreading.thread safety"},{"from":{"fname":"os.memory.ram.spaces.stack","id":"amz8fg5miovqzorc23auu2c","vaultName":"cs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":7,"offset":265},"end":{"line":8,"column":61,"offset":319},"indent":[]},"value":"execution.concurrency.multithreading.thread safety"},{"from":{"fname":"os.memory.ram.user.stack","id":"piezcvnrjdg6yilm1cdyt9h","vaultName":"cs"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":7,"offset":265},"end":{"line":8,"column":61,"offset":319},"indent":[]},"value":"execution.concurrency.multithreading.thread safety"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"f557qwtkau5dfzasxfgnziu","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"thread-safety\">Thread Safety<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#thread-safety\"></a></h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Stateless Implementation\n<ul>\n<li>Source of error in most cases (multithreaded apps)\n<ul>\n<li>Incorrectly sharing state between several threads</li>\n<li>Don't make your methods rely on external state, nor maintain any state at all</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Immutable Implementation\n<ul>\n<li>Need to share states between threads → make them immutable</li>\n<li>Immutable classes = Thread safe</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/3fnxobrsrcrbd4j3v6fz4wz\">Synchronization</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/3uaj7ngwih7npv8vlfs7k6d\">Thread Safety (cs)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/amz8fg5miovqzorc23auu2c\">Stack Space (cs)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/cs/notes/piezcvnrjdg6yilm1cdyt9h\">Stack Space (cs)</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"7ncn3al6mmutkhgoesulce9","title":"Computer Science","desc":"","updated":1715103618849,"created":1713296516553,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"cs"},"contentHash":"36faf26c6be438d4aed355d72b55a110","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"7ncn3al6mmutkhgoesulce9","vaultName":"cs"},"value":"arch","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":3,"offset":105},"end":{"line":6,"column":11,"offset":113},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"arch"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"7ncn3al6mmutkhgoesulce9","vaultName":"cs"},"value":"paradigm","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":3,"offset":159},"end":{"line":11,"column":15,"offset":171},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"paradigm"}}],"anchors":{"references":{"type":"header","text":"References","value":"references","line":23,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["0xgibr34qhbv1edksyoxakk","t246wcci6dy9lnof7l1os4l","71sipcgr0pdqyxnmntvx28w","6k8qk8m6zofpfla0wr8eajn","szmkrtr9ezx1kg3mzcamb7m","a6m88ijp6ij9aam2ose0k6j","7t5m5bvvkqqmexze4ymednf","4bgqfqpix52j5ek9oawj3lw","ng2w78j1rxy1prvsi6zc9j3","q1uj4uy5892ahhlgrn1wi7m","qnetoavqu273jl4iovqtk76","qanoka2zolegyqtrlis4sg2","nsbtaj4zu6fmgjuooy55mbx","uc1prffatcsbivlbj2yud2i","azqmz08s69usdskj1a7v94c","v3e3a8biac8dam